=== repair mode: add refused ===
+ env CLAIMS_REPAIR=1 CLAIMS_INTEGRITY_KEY_FILE=TMPDIR/integrity.key target/release/clms add should refuse
exit=1
Error: add: refusing under CLAIMS_REPAIR=1. repair mode is read-only — it skips claim-integrity verification for forensic recovery (show, diff-evidence, timeline, context). fix the corrupted records first, then unset CLAIMS_REPAIR before mutating state. without this guard, a tampered claim could be carried forward into add/verify/refute/rerun/reindex or archaeology mutation.

